<br>
I guarantee you that if all guilds start acting like this, none of us will ever be able to organize a plane raid, or a raid in any high level zone for that matter.<br>
<br>
I'm talking common sense, unwritten rules and tacit assumptions here. This act was foul and childish. I have no other words for it. This was aimed not only directly at LoM, but to all other guilds that participated in the raid, and the entire guild system on Norrath. <br>
<br>
Basically Lords is saying to all guilds in Norrath: we give you the finger, no matter what you plan, when you planned it and how much work you put into it. Remember this, because this is their message.<br>
